{"tid":1525522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抗爭要轉型！唔好再迷戀佔路設路障既街頭抗爭！立即破壞香港經濟！","createTime":"2019-09-01T01:12:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T16:21:33.000Z","uid":38991,"like":115,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"ec0861e070c3cc649af74bac662a497cdc08820d","tid":1525522,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2778db34b0e6524b0acf1b5780dfa7548ace2c81","tid":1525522,"uid":242083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:12:52.000Z","msg":"831恐襲同721恐襲冇分別<br />\n我正式宣佈香港警察係有牌黑社會兼恐怖分子<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eYzNsiOy00o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeYzNsiOy00o&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8bywbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=af73d5cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eYzNsiOy00o</a>"},{"pid":"8853bd349b9f6587fd6645cf9b94b70dcd3f9575","tid":1525522,"uid":180515,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:14:28.000Z","msg":"遊行沒用了"},{"pid":"21419dcc741e89ee6bab7c566eb537a1927fcdf0","tid":1525522,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:14:51.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"e110b43650a3d022ec6c755b4b5200bf5981db32","tid":1525522,"uid":162499,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ec0861e070c3cc649af74bac662a497cdc08820d","tid":1525522,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:16:18.000Z","msg":"1,罷搭港鐵行動,呢個係最簡單直接既做法(當然你都可以選擇跳閘),改為搭巴士,踩單車,坐渡海小輪甚至行路去返工之類<br />\nQ1:點解冇小巴同的士?<br />\nA1:小巴既話,你唔好忘記上次佔中潮聯單野,的士既話,班愛國的士唔係好明顯啦咩?<br />\n<br />\n2,罷搭港鐵升級版:向其他人(包括遊客),宣傳港鐵過去做過既行動,邀請佢地加入罷搭行動,即使佢地拒絕參與行動,都唔洗惡言相向,我地可以好熱心咁問佢地目的地係邊,然後向佢地推薦去果度既其他方法(推薦其他巴士路線,或者教佢裝九巴,城巴APP之類),記住,呢個係任何地點,任何社交網絡都可以宣傳到<br />\n<br />\n3,罷買港鐵沿線商店及附屬港鐵商場,簡單D黎講,就係拒絕消費,令有關店舖收入大減,若港鐵不減租,店舖必然虧損,自然無法長期經營,最終停止業務,若港鐵減租,則租金收入大減,呢個行動雖然會濫炒到商戶,尤其是港鐵企硬唔減租既話,但係冇辦法,呢個一定要濫炒埋佢<br />\n<br />\n4,抵制地鐵廣告客戶,逼使向港鐵提出終止廣告業務,呢個做法同上次抵制向CCTVB黃金時段落廣告一樣,所以我唔再重複<br />\n<br />\n呢4個行動,係我暫時諗到係香港人可以即時做到既野,記住,呢個係長期戰爭,係唔可能1日就成功"},{"pid":"245bff079958b82606c58b0b5077f0b017950a3b","tid":1525522,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ed1a3a3eae16f103b0faf0304b08dcbd7a8be42","tid":1525522,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:18:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b56456040eb7639f138cdeeb405d0b52cd99edb","tid":1525522,"uid":4174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:19:23.000Z","msg":"仲有CCTVB"},{"pid":"4315d5e078390a2294e3d248c10edd7de495b3ac","tid":1525522,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:19:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"edfe0572a8c4541ba76dcb6c4c43b5524c1ac0e3","tid":1525522,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:19:33.000Z","msg":"大破壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c268113973f45c632b2d50ad8ef6d1642d52bcda","tid":1525522,"uid":255402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f2f18714405db3b819496180ca5b997b165717a","tid":1525522,"uid":265498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:20:03.000Z","msg":"[901和你飛］作戰任務地點！！！職員爆料，一，二號檢查閘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524355\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524355</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b0a739932e14eede50583372976f694ae4401bce","tid":1525522,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:20:38.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid