8991,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a83c2c70c3128e845be00bb800a66cd9e9571d14","tid":1525522,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:26:58.000Z","msg":"私人地方佢地會玩禁制令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b5ac06f9e16d28ea150d1def01324f7eee00db8","tid":1525522,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:34:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77e54af2662ab894c1fdac4f871b54623c1aab3d","tid":1525522,"uid":258258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:38:05.000Z","msg":"老實講唔明點解迷戀街頭戰，而家我地係有目的地等待(eg 10.1、美國國會)，保持國際聲音同保存人力、物力係最重要任務，點解唔簡安全D又影響經濟既機埸抗爭？ 我諗有D人覺得唔上街頭冇D爆既畫面keep 唔到noise 做唔到文宣，但我唔認為真心支持我地陣營要靠咁樣留住，相大型街頭戰基本有人被捕係無可避免，其實小不免會打擊士氣。至於文宣，其實之前D核爆文宣好多都未完全散播，有D英文都未翻譯。都係個句，我唔係叫大家停戰，不過要簡適合既戰埸，除非有特別目標(eg 拆燈柱)，如果唔係街頭戰應該避免。因為一有人發起街頭戰，有D手足就算知危險/唔主張街戰既，為左夠人互相cover都照出，所以希望發起任務手足諗清楚目標，成本效益先好號召，手足真係每次搭條命入去做任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52467d91cf922da8baf6ec31cab8b3810bdc789e","tid":1525522,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec2c41bb0f635b7166f1e996a4199cd93193fee","tid":1525522,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:43:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c8817134901eeb229bf7b6fcaedb2a45a62e9a1","tid":1525522,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa6d157aa36be9cce9d893b1642995b4cef2db56","tid":1525522,"uid":193233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score